comments: Conley (UTA) turns to go over the pick and marginal body contact occurs with Jones' (MEM) side.
Melton (MEM) touches the ball last prior to it going out of bounds.
Gobert (UTA) turns slightly toward Jackson Jr. (MEM) and marginal body contact occurs prior to Gobert blocking the driving shot attempt.
House Jr. (UTA) and Bane (MEM) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Gobert (UTA) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in House Jr.'s (UTA) path and absorbs the contact.

Williams (MEM) brings his left arm out toward Gobert's (UTA) path and he absorbs the marginal contact as the defensive switch occurs. Williams and Gobert engage and disengage with one another thereafter.
Bogdanovic (UTA) is retreating away from Jackson Jr. (MEM) and marginal contact occurs with Jackson Jr.'s slightly extended right arm as he starts his upward shooting motion.
Jones (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away as simultaneous incidental contact occurs with Conley (UTA) and Gobert (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) dives to the floor in pursuit of the loose ball and incidental body contact occurs with Jones (MEM).
Bane (MEM) is extending to the side and does not establish a legal guarding position prior to body contact occurring with Mitchell (UTA) during the drive.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) firms up over his left foot and absorbs the side-to-side contact that occurs with Conley (UTA) as the screen is set.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) moves forward toward Gobert (UTA) and marginal contact occurs with Gobert's back after he receives the pass.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) initiates contact across Gobert's (UTA) right forearm and causes Gobert to lose control of the ball during his upward shooting motion.
Gobert (UTA) grasps and then quickly releases Bane's (MEM) left arm as he begins rolling into the lane.
Bane (MEM) wraps Gobert's (UTA) upper half off-ball.
Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) right leg slightly extends outward after the release and marginal contact occurs with Gobert (UTA) following Gobert's shot contest.

Bane (MEM) moves slightly forward toward Mitchell (UTA) and marginal body contact occurs after Mitchell's gather. Bane follows-through on his shot contest and marginal contact occurs with Mitchell's right hand after the release. Anderson (MEM) then cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Jones (MEM) brings his off-arm toward House Jr.'s (UTA) side and marginal contact occurs as House Jr.'s momentum continues to carry him toward the baseline.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Conley (UTA) and Jones (MEM) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Gobert (UTA) briefly has his hands around Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) midsection before correcting.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) and House Jr. (UTA) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
O'Neale (UTA) and Anderson (MEM) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
O'Neale (UTA) legally contests Anderson's (MEM) put-back attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) and Williams (MEM) legally contest Mitchell's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Conley's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact.
